Revision history for Spoejs.

0.02
  New features:
  - Mixing text+media support
  - Visual text+media mixing editor
  - Movie clip support
  - Syndication
  - Translator mode
  - Right and left columns
  - Annotations
  - Comments
  - Humantest
  - YAML for text storage
  - Tabbed configuration pages for site, journal and story
  Bug fixes:
  - Wording changes: Channel->Journal
  - Maxside->diagonal for scaling media
  - Encrypted passwords
  - Sorting by date

0.01  Fri Apr  9 00:37:15 2004
  - Original version
  - Perl modules for storage
  - Bootstring encoded url's and filenames
  - Multi-lingual menus and stories
  - Picture support
  - Icons
  - Theme layer
  - Registration
  - Site Administration
  - Media page, story page, story-list page, channel list page
  - Picture upload
  - Import pictures from local-disk
